    <fluff>
        <overview>When Clan Jade Falcon recaptured Pandora from the Lyran Commonwealth they found their old production line building a new Hunchback IIC variant. Hoping to make a “sensible” Hunchback IIC, the Lyrans used pulse lasers and LB 20-X autocannons to maintain an improved heat curve while almost doubling the killing potential of their own Hunchbacks. With Red Devil Industries back in Falcon hands, the Hunchback IIC 5 is a common sight on the Steiner front. Its nature forces the Lyrans to employ Clan-like quick, decisive strikes.</overview>
